<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse majandus- ja sotsiaalkomitee arvamust, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the opinion of the Committee of the Regions(4), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse regioonide komitee arvamust ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Whereas the conclusions of the Luxembourg European Council of 12 and 13 December 1997 provide for an enhanced pre-accession strategy for the applicant countries of central and eastern Europe, and a specific pre-accession strategy for Cyprus; </inglise>
<eesti> 1) Euroopa &Uuml;lemkogu 12. ja 13. detsembri 1997. aasta Luxembourgi istungj&auml;rgu otsustega n&auml;hakse ette t&otilde;hustatud &uuml;hinemiseelne strateegia Kesk- ja Ida-Euroopa kandidaatriikide jaoks ning &uuml;hinemiseelne eristrateegia K&uuml;prose jaoks; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Whereas the conclusions of the Luxembourg European Council of 12 and 13 December 1997 provide that the assistance provided for in this Regulation is to be granted for the time being to the 10 applicant countries of central and eastern Europe; </inglise>
<eesti> 2) Euroopa &Uuml;lemkogu 12. ja 13. detsembri 1997. aasta Luxembourgi istungj&auml;rgu otsustes s&auml;testatakse, et k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud abi antakse praegu k&uuml;mnele Kesk- ja Ida-Euroopa kandidaatriigile; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) Whereas Council Regulation (EC) No 622/98 of 16 March 1998 on assistance to the applicant States in the framework of the pre-accession strategy, and in particular on the establishment of Accession Partnerships(5), provides that those partnerships are to comprise a single framework for the priority areas and all available resources for pre-accession assistance; </inglise>
<eesti> 3) n&otilde;ukogu 16. m&auml;rtsi 1998. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 622/98 (&uuml;hinemiseelse strateegia raames kandidaatriikidele antava abi kohta ja eelk&otilde;ige &uuml;hinemispartnerluse loomise kohta) n&auml;hakse ette, et partnerlus sisaldab &uuml;htset raamistikku esmat&auml;htsate valdkondade kohta ning k&otilde;iki &uuml;hinemiseelseks abiks kasutada olevaid ressursse; </eesti>
<inglise> (4) Whereas the pre-accession strategy includes provision for an Instrument for Structural Policies for Pre-accession (ISPA), which will be directed towards aligning applicant countries on Community infrastructure standards and provide a financial contribution for environmental measures, and transport infrastructure measures; </inglise>
<eesti> 4) &uuml;hinemiseelses strateegias on ette n&auml;htud &uuml;hinemiseelse struktuuripoliitika rahastamisvahend (Instrument for Structural Policies for Pre-Accession - ISPA), mille eesm&auml;rgiks on viia kandidaatriigid vastavusse &uuml;henduse infrastruktuuristandarditega ja anda rahalist toetust keskkonnakaitse- ja transpordiinfrastruktuurimeetmetele; </eesti>
<inglise> (5) Whereas assistance from the Community under ISPA, together with assistance from the Community under Council Regulation (EEC) No 3906/89 of 18 December 1989 on economic aid to the Republic of Hungary and the Polish People's Republic(6), and assistance from the Community under Council Regulation (EC) No 1268/1999 of 21 June 1999 on Community support for pre-accession measures for agricultural and rural development in the applicant countries of central and eastern Europe in the pre-accession period(7) is to be coordinated within the framework of Council Regulation (EC) No 1266/1999 of 21 June 1999 on coordinating aid to the applicant countries in the framework of the pre-accession strategy and amending Regulation (EEC) No 3906/89(8) and to be subject to the conditionality provisions of Regulation (EC) No 622/98 and of the individual decisions on Accession Partnerships; </inglise>
<eesti> 5) ISPA kaudu antav &uuml;henduse abi, n&otilde;ukogu 18. detsembri 1989. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3906/89 (Ungari Vabariigile ja Poola Rahvavabariigile antava majandusabi kohta) alusel antav &uuml;henduse abi ja n&otilde;ukogu 21. juuni 1999. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1268/1999 (&uuml;henduse toetuse kohta &uuml;hinemiseelsetele meetmetele p&otilde;llumajanduse ja maapiirkondade arendamiseks Kesk- ja Ida-Euroopa kandidaatriikides &uuml;hinemiseelsel perioodil) alusel antav abi tuleb koosk&otilde;lastada n&otilde;ukogu 21. juuni 1999. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1266/1999 (kandidaatriikidele &uuml;hinemiseelse strateegia raames antava abi koosk&otilde;lastamise ja m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3906/89 muutmise kohta) ning selle suhtes kohaldatakse m&auml;&auml;ruses (E&Uuml;) nr 622/98 ja &uuml;hinemispartnerluse kohta tehtud &uuml;ksikotsustes etten&auml;htud tingimuslikkuse s&auml;tteid; </eesti>
<inglise> (6) Whereas an equal balance should be the aim between financing for transport infrastructure measures and financing for environmental measures, taking into account the specific situations in the beneficiary countries; </inglise>
<eesti> 6) eesm&auml;rk on saavutada tasakaal transpordiinfrastruktuurimeetmete ja keskkonnakaitsemeetmete rahastamise vahel, v&otilde;ttes arvesse abi saavate riikide konkreetseid olusid; </eesti>
<inglise> (7) Whereas the Community assistance under ISPA should facilitate the implementation by the applicant countries of the acquis communautaire in the field of the environment and contribute to sustainable development in these countries; </inglise>
