<inglise> (8) Whereas Decision No 1692/96/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of23 July 1996 on Community guidelines for the development of the trans-European transport network(9) describes the criteria for projects of common interest, which should be used, where appropriate, for selecting the measures eligible under this Regulation; </inglise>
